- Left figures alone as requested.
- No duplicate abstract/body abstract was found, so no abstract removal was needed.

Self-check:
- Paragraph boundaries now use blank lines where intended.
- In-text equation references of the form `(x-y)` now have corresponding tagged display equations in the document.


